# Development Log

> Compass §3.2 / §5 tracking doc. Append every time you finish a slice, make a decision, or hit a PRD problem.
> Example entries are greyed with `>`. Just fill in the blank template below.

---

## Decision Record

> Record major technical/design decisions made during development (date / decision / rationale).

> **Example (greyed example, do not keep)**
> - **2026-06-09** — Use SQLite instead of PostgreSQL
>   - Rationale: single-machine deployment, no concurrent-write need, saves DB server ops cost; can migrate later.

- **<date YYYY-MM-DD>** — <decision>
  - Rationale: <why this choice; note trade-offs if any>

