## PRD Issues (§5.1.2 [SKIPPED-PRD] bugs awaiting ruling)

> The PRD itself has a bug / self-contradiction: stop, log, await user ruling, **do not edit the PRD yourself**.

> **Example (greyed example)**
> - `[SKIPPED-PRD]` **§4.2 vs §6.1 conflict** — §4.2 says amount can be negative, §6.1 says amount ≥ 0.
>   - Status: await ruling
>   - Impact: payment validation logic temporarily uses §6.1 (≥ 0) as a stopgap, fix after ruling.

- `[SKIPPED-PRD]` **<§section + conflict description>** — <bug content>
  - Status: await ruling
  - Impact: <how it's handled for now / what's blocked>

