## PRD Gaps (§5.1.3 gap enhancement awaiting ruling)

> Not in the PRD, but during implementation you find "adding it would be better": keep the implementation, log, await ruling.
> **Don't just apply YAGNI and cut it** — leave it to the user to decide.

> **Example (greyed example)**
> - **Export missing field** — PRD export doesn't include "created time", which reports commonly need.
>   - Implemented: temporarily added `created_at` field to export CSV.
>   - Status: await ruling (keep / remove)

- **<topic>** — <the PRD gap and why adding it is better>
  - Implemented: <what I did>
  - Status: await ruling (keep / remove)

